data.description: Premium 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home nestled in Helotes with a scenic view of expansive hills. Located in a spacious cul-de-sac. Built with comfort and convenience in mind with an impressive floor plan. Large scaled game room with lots of upgrades. The primary bedroom is over-sized and has a sprawling deluxe bathroom. A must see.  This home has so much opportunity. The area is conveniently located between Seaworld and Six Flags. Easily accessible to Walmart, HEB, and retail stores.
